title: Wooden Cutlery
description:
This Japanese style bamboo wooden cutlery set is composed of a fork, knife, spoon and chopsticks. 
They are bundled in a beautifully crafted tied line bag that will facilitate transportation and allows to be stored in a hand bag, gym bag or bag pack.  
Zero waste bamboo cutlery set can be taken outside home for a day out or for longer travel time. 
The inside of the line bag is made of water proof material as a consequence you can pack your cutlery set still wet which is convenient if you cannot dry them. 
Design in a high  to please adults and children alike.
